summary:
I don't even think there's a chance that's gonna happen but
what if Caleb gets so focused on his pursuit of knowledge that he...
body:
I don’t even think there’s a chance that’s gonna happen but

what if Caleb gets so focused on his pursuit of knowledge that he becomes more and more selfish and willing to sacrifice everything for it?

I’m talking like. Full on evil Caleb.

He kills some of the party when they try to stop him and convinces himself it won’t matter what he does because he’ll turn back time eventually.

And he does awful fucking things. Becomes incredibly powerful. Multiple parties of adventurers try to stop him.

But eventually… eventually he succeeds. And he saves his parents.

But he can’t save himself anymore.
